\id 1JN 1 JEAN SOSO scy/cdb 2003
\h Yaya I
\toc1 Ala xa masenyi singe Annabi Yaya naxan s…õb…õ
\toc2 Yaya I
\mt1 Ala xa masenyi singe
\mt1 Annabi Yaya naxan s…õb…õ
\imt1 Masenyi nde yi Kitaabui xa fe ra
\ip Annabi Yaya naxan yi bataax…õ s…õb…õ, a nu na Isa xa x…õ…õra fu nun firinyie nan ya ma. A naxa Inyila Isa s…õb…õ, a man naxa bataax…õ saxan s…õb…õ danxaniyat…î…õe b…õ, alako e xa Ala xa l…înni nun limaniya s…ît…î. A d…înx…î…õ ra, Annabi Yaya naxa Kitaabui nde s…õb…õ naxan xili ¬´Ala xa Waxayi.¬ª A na s…õb…õ Isayankae nan ma naxee nu na …≤axankat…õ s…ît…îfe e xa danxaniya xa fe ra.
\ip Yi bataax…õ singe s…õb…õ n…õ Isayankae ma alako e naxa e madaxu wule xaranyi ra, naxan nu yensenxi na waxati, a falafe ra Isa mu nu faxi duni…≤a a adama ki ma. Annabi Yaya a masenxi a Isa findixi adamadi yati yati nan na, Ala naxan x…õ…õxi kelife koore ma a sago rabafe ma. Isa fatanxi Ala nan na, k…în…î Ala naxa a ragiri a xa findi x…õm…õ ra duni…≤a b…õnd…õ fu…≤i fari, alako a xa n…î a y…õt…õ bade s…õr…õx…õ ra ibunadama b…õ.
\ip Isa xa s…õr…õx…õ tide gbo adama b…õ, barima na gbansan n…îma a niyade adamadie xa kisi s…ît…î. Mixi naxan bara kisi s…ît…î Isa wuli saabui ra, a a kolon a b…î…≤…õ kui a a kisixi abadan. Siik…õ yo mu luma a yi ra s…în…în, barima a a kolon Ala fama n…õ a xa laayidi rakamalide.
\ip Na s…õr…õx…õ man findima misaali ra danxaniyat…î…õe b…õ. Annabi Yaya a masenma a won xa won bore xanu al…î Ala won xanuxi ki nax…õ. Ala wama a f…îxirabir…õe xa findi mixie ra naxee e bore xanuma. Mixi naxan a falama a Ala xanuma, k…în…î a mu a boore ibunadama xanuxi, na kanyi bara findi wule fal…õ ra.
\ip Ala kolonfe munafanyi gbo adama b…õ. Na n…îma a niyade a xa ariyanna s…ît…î yare, a man xa duni…≤…õigiri fanyi s…ît…î be. Ala xa won mali a xa xanunteya kolonfe ra, alako won xa kisi s…ît…î, won man xa findi mixie ra naxee e bore xanuxi. Amina.
\mt1 Ala xa masenyi singe
\mt1 Annabi Yaya naxan s…õb…õ
\cl Sora
\c 1
\s1 Kisi Masenyi
\q1 
\v 1 Kisi masenyi,
\q1 naxan nu na kabi a f…îl…õ,
\q1 muxu tuli naxan m…õxi,
\q1 muxu ya naxan toxi,
\q1 muxu b…õl…õx…õ naxan masuxuxi,
\q1 muxu bara na seede ba.
\q1 
\v 2 Naxan na kisi ra, na bara a y…õt…õ masen.
\q1 Muxu bara a to,
\q1 muxu bara na kisi xa fe kawandi ti,
\q1 naxan mu …≤…înma abadan,
\q1 naxan nu na Baba Ala f…õ ma,
\q1 beenun a xa a y…õt…õ masen muxu b…õ.
\q1 
\v 3 Muxu naxan toxi,
\q1 muxu naxan m…õxi,
\q1 muxu wo fan kawandife na nan na,
\q1 alako won birin xa lu lanyi kui,
\q1 won nun Baba Ala nun a xa Di Isa, a xa Mixi Sugandixi.
\q1 
\v 4 Muxu yi fe s…õb…õfe n…õ wo ma,
\q1 alako muxu xa s…õ…õw…õ xa kamali.
\p 
\v 5 Muxu naxan m…õxi Isa ra, muxu xa na d…õnt…õg…õ sa wo b…õ. Ala findixi naiyalanyi nan na. Dimi yo mu na a i.
\v 6 Xa won a fala won nun Ala na a ra, k…în…î won …≤…õr…õma dimi kui, won bara wule fala, won mu …≤…õr…õfe n…îndi kira x…în ma.
\v 7 K…în…î, xa won …≤…õr…õma naiyalanyi kui Ala xa kira x…în, won nun danxaniyat…î…õe nan luma lanyi kui. Ala xa Di Isa wuli nan won nas…õniy…õnma yunubi birin ma.
\p 
\v 8 Xa won a fala yunubi yo mu na won ma, won bara won y…õt…õ madaxu, n…îndi yo mu na won b…õ.
\v 9 Xa won na won ti won ma yunubie ra, Ala e xafarima n…õ, a won nas…õniy…õn won ma tinxintareya ma. Ala tinxin, won n…îma won xaxili tide a ra.
\v 10 Xa won a fala yunubi yo mu na won ma, won bara Ala findi wule fal…õ ra, a xa masenyi mu na won b…î…≤…õ kui.
\c 2
\s1 Won xunmafalama
\p 
\v 1 N ma die, n bara na birin s…õb…õ wo ma, alako wo naxa yunubi raba, k…în…î xa a sa li mixi nde naxa bira na kui, Ala xa Mixi Sugandixi Isa fama won xunmafalade Baba Ala b…õ. Isa tinxin.
\v 2 A tan nan findixi s…õr…õx…õ ra won ma yunubie xafarife ra. A mu won ma yunubie gbansan xafarixi, a na nan nabaxi duni…≤a mixi birin b…õ.
\p 
\v 3 Xa won sa Ala xa yaamarie rabatu, na nan a masenma a won Ala kolon.
\v 4 Xa mixi nde a fala, ¬´N tan Ala kolon¬ª, k…în…î a mu a xa yaamarie rabatuma, wule fal…õ nan a ra, n…îndi mu na a b…õ.
\v 5 K…în…î mixi naxan Ala xui suxuma, Ala xa xanunteya bara g…õ kamalide na kanyi b…õ. Na kui, won n…îma a kolonde won na Ala f…îx…î ra.
\v 6 Naxan yo a falama a nun Ala nan a ra, a lanma a xa a …≤…õr…õ Isa xa kira x…în.
\p 
\v 7 N xanuntenyie, n yaamari naxan masenma wo b…õ, fe n…õ…õn…õ mu a ra. Wo a kolon kabi a f…îl…õ. Yaamari fori nan a ra, wo naxan singe m…õ nu.
\v 8 K…în…î i man na mato n yaamari n…õ…õn…õ nan s…õb…õfe wo ma. N…îndi nan a ra naxan mak…õn…õnxi Isa …≤…õr…õ ki kui a nun wo tan fan …≤…õr…õ ki kui, barima dimi na …≤…înfe, Ala xa naiyalanyi laxix…õ bara mini f…îl…î.
\p 
\v 9 Naxan a falama a a na Ala xa naiyalanyi kui, k…în…î a a ngaxakerenyi x…înxi, na kanyi man na dimi nan kui.
\v 10 Naxan a ngaxakerenyi xanuma, na kanyi sabatixi Ala xa naiyalanyi nan kui, fefe mu na naxan a rabirama.
\v 11 K…în…î naxan a ngaxakerenyi x…înma, na kanyi na dimi nan kui. A …≤…õr…õma dimi nan kui, a mu a sigade yati toma, barima dimi bara a ya d…înxu.
\q1 
\v 12 N ma die, n xa a masen wo b…õ yi s…õb…õli ra:
\q1 Wo xa yunubie bara xafari Isa xili saabui ra.
\q1 
\v 13 Forie, n xa a masen wo b…õ yi s…õb…õli ra:
\q1 Wo bara a kolon a tan naxan nu na kabi a f…îl…õ.
\q1 Fonikee, n xa a masen wo b…õ yi s…õb…õli ra: Wo bara n…î Sentan…õ ra.
\q1 
\v 14 N ma die, n bara na masen wo b…õ yi s…õb…õli ra,
\q1 barima wo bara Baba Ala kolon.
\q1 Forie, n bara na masen wo b…õ yi s…õb…õli ra,
\q1 barima wo a kolon naxan na na kabi a f…îl…õ.
\p Fonikee, n bara na masen wo b…õ yi s…õb…õli ra:
\q1 barima wo s…õnb…õ gbo.
\q1 Ala xa masenyi sabatixi wo b…î…≤…õ kui.
\q1 Wo bara n…î…õ s…ît…î Sentan…õ xun ma.
\p 
\v 15 Wo naxa duni…≤a fe xanu, xa na mu a ra wo mu n…îma Baba Ala xanude.
\v 16 Naxan findixi duni…≤a fe ra, al…î ibunadama wax…înfe kobi, mil…õ, nun y…õt…õ igbo…≤a naxan kelixi see s…ît…îfe ma, na sese mu kelixi Baba Ala ma. A kelixi yi duni…≤a nan ma.
\v 17 Duni…≤a nun a wax…înfe …≤…înma n…õ, k…în…î naxee Ala wax…înfe rabama, e kisima n…õ abadan.
\s1 Ala xa Mixi Sugandixi yaxui
\p 
\v 18 N ma die, won na waxati d…înx…î…õ n…õ yi ki. Wo bara a m…õ, a Ala xa Mixi Sugandixi yaxui nde na fafe. Wo bara a kolon a yaxui gbegbe bara fa. Won a kolon na nan ma a won na waxati d…înx…î…õ n…õ yi ki.
\v 19 Na mixie kelixi won tan nan xun ma, k…în…î won ngaxakerenyi mu nu e ra, xa na mu a ra e mu nu kelima won xun ma nu. K…în…î e to mu tin lude won ya ma, e bara a masen a won ngaxakerenyie mu nu e ra.
\p 
\v 20 Ala xa S…õniy…õnt…î…õ bara wo sugandi, a Xaxili S…õniy…õnxi fi wo ma. Na nan a toxi wo birin n…îndi kolonxi.
\v 21 N mu yi bataax…õ s…õb…õxi wo ma wo xa n…îndi kolontareya xa ma. N a s…õb…õxi wo xa n…îndi kolonyi xa fe nan ma, wule yo mu na naxan kui.
\p 
\v 22 Wule fal…õ na nde ra? Naxan a falama a Isa mu findixi Ala xa Mixi Sugandixi ra. Na kanyi bara findi Ala xa Mixi Sugandixi yaxui ra. A bara tondi Baba Ala nun a xa Di ra.
\v 23 Mixi naxan tondima Ala xa Di ra, a bara tondi Baba Ala fan na. Naxan bara tin Ala xa Di ra, a bara tin Baba Ala fan na.
\p 
\v 24 Wo masenyi naxan m…õ a f…îl…õ, wo xa na ragata wo b…î…≤…õ ma. Xa a na na ki n…õ, a lima wo bara sabati Baba Ala xa Di nun Baba Ala i.
\v 25 Ala xa Mixi Sugandixi bara kisi laayidi tongo won b…õ, kisi naxan mu …≤…înma abadan.
\p 
\v 26 N bara yi bataax…õ s…õb…õ wo ma mixi ndee nan ma fe ra naxee wama wo madaxufe.
\v 27 Ala bara a Xaxili fi wo ma, a na wo b…î…≤…õ i. Wo hayi mu na karam…îx…î gb…õt…õ ma. Ala Xaxili nan wo matinkanma n…îndi birin na. Wule yo mu na a xa masenyi kui. Wo xa bira a f…îx…î ra tun.
\p 
\v 28 N ma die, wo nun Isa xa lu a ra, alako a na gbilen t…õmui nax…õ yaagi yo naxa won makuya a ra. Won xa la a ra t…õmui birin.
\v 29 Wo to a kolon a tinxin, wo xa a kolon fan a tinxint…î…õ birin fatanxi a tan nan na.
\c 3
\s1 Ala xa die
\p 
\v 1 Wo xa a kolon, Baba Ala won xanuxi n…õ han a won xili ¬´a xa die¬ª. Won findixi a xa die yati yati nan na. Duni…≤a mu n…îma won kolonde na ra, barima e mu Ala kolon.
\v 2 N xanuntenyie, yak…îsi Ala xa die nan won na. A mu masenxi sinden won luma ki nax…õ, k…în…î won a kolon, a Isa na fa, won masarama n…õ, won fa lu al…î a tan, barima won a toma n…õ a na ki nax…õ yati.
\v 3 Mixi naxan a yigi tixi Isa ra, a a y…õt…õ ras…õniy…õnma, al…î Isa s…õniy…õnxi ki nax…õ.
\p 
\v 4 Mixi naxan yunubi rabama, a findixi s…õriy…õ matandila nan na, barima yunubi, s…õriy…õ matandi nan a ra.
\v 5 Wo a kolon a Isa fa won ma yunubi nan xafaride. Yunubi yo mu nu na a tan ma.
\v 6 Mixi naxan sabatixi Isa i, na kanyi mu luma yunubi raba ra s…în…în. Naxan luma yunubi raba ra, na kanyi mu Isa toxi, a man mu a kolon.
\p 
\v 7 N ma die, mixi yo naxa wo madaxu. Mixi naxan tinxinyi rabama, a tinxin al…î Marigi tinxinxi ki nax…õ.
\v 8 Yunubit…î…õ tan fatanxi Ibulisa nan na, barima Ibulisa nan yunubi raba kabi duni…≤a f…îl…õ. Ala xa Di fa n…õ alako a xa Ibulisa xa wali kana.
\p 
\v 9 Mixi yo findi Ala xa di ra, a mu luma yunubi raba ra, barima Ala bara wali nde f…îl…î a b…î…≤…õ kui. A mu n…îma lude yunubi kui, barima a fatanxi Ala nan na.
\v 10 Ala xa die nun Ibulisa xa die tagi rasama yi ki n…õ: Naxan mu tinxin, Ala xa di mu a ra. Naxan mu a boore adamadie xanuma, a mu Ala kolon.
\s1 Xanunteya
\p 
\v 11 Masenyi nan ya wo naxan m…õxi kabi a f…îl…õ: Won xa won bore xanu.
\v 12 Won naxa lu al…î Kabila, naxan fatan Sentan…õ ra, a fa a xunya yati faxa. A na raba munfe ra? A na raba n…õ barima a …≤…õr…õ ki mu nu g…õxi tinxinde al…î a xunya …≤…õr…õ ki.
\p 
\v 13 N ngaxakerenyie, wo naxa wo ma…≤in duni…≤a xa x…înnanteya xa fe ra wo mabiri.
\v 14 Xanunteya naxan luma won b…î…≤…õ kui won boore adamadie b…õ, a a masenma a won bara fax…õ kira lu na, won ti kisi kira x…în ma. Xanunteyatare tan tixi fax…õ kira nan x…în ma.
\v 15 Mixi naxan a boore adamadi x…înma, na kanyi luxi n…õ al…î fax…õti. Wo a kolon a kisi mu na fax…õti b…õ.
\p 
\v 16 Won xanunteya kolonma Ala xa Mixi Sugandixi Isa xa misaali nan saabui ra, naxan tinxi a nii fide won b…õ. Won fan lan n…õ won xa tin na rabade won boore adamadie b…õ.
\v 17 Se kanyi naxan a b…î…≤…õ balanma t…î…îr…îmixi ya ra, a mu Ala xa xanunteya kolon.
\v 18 N ma die, won ma xanunteya naxa findi w…îy…õnyi tun na, a xa findi maraba nan na, xa na mu a ra n…îndi yo mu na a kui.
\p 
\v 19 Na kui, won n…îma a kolonde a n…îndi na won yi, won b…î…≤…õ fa sa Ala mabiri.
\v 20 Hali won b…î…≤…õ sa won makiiti, Ala gbo won b…î…≤…õ b…õ, a fe birin kolon.
\v 21 N xanuntenyie, xa won b…î…≤…õ mu won makiiti, won bara xaxilisa s…ît…î Ala ya i.
\v 22 Ala won ma duba birin suxuma n…õ, barima won birama a xa s…õriy…õe nun a wax…înfe nan f…îx…î ra.
\p 
\v 23 A xa s…õriy…õ nan ya: Won xa danxaniya a xa Di ma, a xa Mixi Sugandixi Isa. Won man xa won bore xanu, al…î Ala won yamarixi ki nax…õ.
\v 24 Mixi naxan Ala xa s…õriy…õ rabatuma, na kanyi nun Ala na a ra. A a kolonma Ala Xaxili S…õniy…õnxi nan ma, Ala naxan fixi won ma.
\c 4
\s1 Tagi rasa Ala Xaxili nun Sentan…õ Xaxili
\p 
\v 1 N xanuntenyie, wo naxa la xaxili birin na. Wo xa a mato a fanyi ra xa na xaxili fatanxi Ala nan na, barima wule fal…õe bara gbo duni…≤a naxee e y…õt…õ findixi nami…≤…înm…õe ra.
\v 2 Mixi naxan birin laxi a ra a Ala xa Mixi Sugandixi Isa bara fa duni…≤a ma a adama ki ma, wo n…îma n…õ a kolonde a na kanyi tan xaxili fatanxi Ala nan na.
\v 3 K…în…î mixi naxan birin mu laxi Isa ra, na gbe xaxili mu fatanxi Ala ra, a fatanxi Ala xa Mixi Sugandixi yaxui nan na, wo bara naxan ma fe m…õ, a a na fafe duni…≤a ma. N xa a fala wo b…õ, a …≤an bara fa.
\p 
\v 4 N ma die, wo tan, Ala nan gbe wo ra. Wo bara n…î na nami…≤…înm…õ wule fal…õe ra, barima Ala Xaxili naxan na wo f…îx…î ra, na s…õnb…õ gbo Sentan…õ xaxili b…õ naxan na duni…≤a mixie f…îx…î ra.
\v 5 E tan duni…≤a nan gbe e ra. Na nan a ra e w…îy…õnma duni…≤a ki ma, duni…≤a fa e xui suxu.
\v 6 K…în…î won tan, Ala nan gbe won na. Na nan a ra Ala kolonyie won xui suxuma. Ala kolontaree tan mu won xui suxuma. N…îndi xaxili nun wule xaxili tagi rasama na ki n…õ.
\s1 Xanunteya fatanma Ala nan na
\q1 
\v 7 N xanuntenyie, won xa won bore xanu,
\q1 barima xanunteya fatanxi Ala nan na.
\q1 Mixi naxan a boore adamadi xanuma,
\q1 na bara findi Ala xa di ra, a Ala kolon.
\q1 
\v 8 Mixi naxan mu a boore adamadi xanuma,
\q1 na kanyi mu Ala kolon,
\q1 barima Ala, xanunteya nan a ra.
\q1 
\v 9 Ala xa xanunteya kolonma yi nan ma:
\q1 Ala naxa a xa Di kerenyi x…õ…õ duni…≤a,
\q1 alako won xa kisi a tan saabui ra.
\q1 
\v 10 Xanunteya yati yati nan ya:
\q1 Won tan xa mu Ala xanuxi,
\q1 a tan nan won xanuxi,
\q1 a fa a xa Di kerenyi x…õ…õ
\q1 a xa findi won ma yunubi xafari s…õr…õx…õ ra.
\p 
\v 11 N xanuntenyie, Ala to bara won xanu na ki, won fan lan n…õ won xa won bore xanu.
\v 12 Mixi yo mu na naxan Ala toxi, k…în…î xa won won bore xanu, Ala luma n…õ won i. A xa xanunteya kamalima n…õ won i.
\p 
\v 13 Won a kolon won nun Ala na a ra, barima a bara a Xaxili fi won ma.
\v 14 Muxu tan bara a to, muxu bara findi seede ra, a Baba Ala a xa Di x…õ…õ n…õ duni…≤a ma adamadie rakiside.
\v 15 Mixi naxan a falama a Isa findixi Ala xa Di nan na, na kanyi nun Ala na a ra.
\v 16 Won bara Ala xa xanunteya kolon, won bara la a ra. Ala findixi xanunteya nan na. Mixi naxan …≤…õr…õma xanunteya kui, na kanyi nun Ala na a ra.
\p 
\v 17 Na kui, xanunteya bara kamali won tagi, alako gaaxui naxa lu won yi ra kiitisa l…îx…î…õ, barima won birama Isa xa misaali f…îx…î ra yi duni…≤a b…õnd…õ fu…≤i fari.
\v 18 Gaaxui mu luma xanuntenyie tagi xa e xa xanunteya bara kamali. Mixi gaaxuma …≤axankat…õ nan xa fe ra, k…în…î xanunteya kamalixi kanyi mu gaaxuma.
\v 19 Won n…îma mixi xanude, barima Ala singe nan bara won xanu.
\v 20 Mixi naxan a falama a Ala xanuxi, k…în…î a luma mixi x…în na, na kanyi bara findi wule fal…õ ra. Mixi naxan mu fata a boore adamadi xanude a naxan toma, na mu n…îma Ala xanude a mu naxan toxi.
\v 21 Ala won yamarixi yi nan na: Naxan Ala xanuxi, a xa nu a boore adamadi fan xanu.
\c 5
\s1 Danxaniyafe Ala xa Di ma
\p 
\v 1 Mixi naxan lama a ra a Isa nan findixi Ala xa Mixi Sugandixi ra, na kanyi bara findi Ala xa di ra. Naxan bab…õ nde xanuma, a na bab…õ xa di fan xanuma n…õ.
\v 2 Won na Ala xanu, won fa a xa yaamari birin nabatu, na nan a masenma a won Ala xa die fan xanuma.
\v 3 Ala xanufe a niyama won xa a xa yaamarie fan nabatu. Na mu findima kote x…îr…îx…î…õ ra,
\v 4 barima Ala xa die n…îma duni…≤a birin na e xa danxaniya saabui ra.
\v 5 Nde xunnakeli s…ît…îma duni…≤a xun na, xa danxaniyat…î…õ mu a ra, naxan lama a ra a Ala xa Di nan Isa ra?
\p 
\v 6 Ala xa Mixi Sugandixi Isa nan fa ye nun wuli ra. A mu faxi ye gbansan xa ra, a faxi ye nun wuli nan na. Ala Xaxili nan na seede baxi, barima Ala Xaxili n…îndi nan a ra.
\v 7 Seede saxan nan na:
\v 8 Ala Xaxili S…õniy…õnxi, ye, nun wuli. Na saxanyi birin seede…≤…îx…îya keren nan bama.
\v 9 Won tinma mixie xa seede…≤…îx…îya ra, k…în…î Ala xa seede…≤…îx…îya dangi na birin na. Ala nan seede bama a xa Di xa fe ra.
\v 10 Mixi naxan lama Ala xa seede…≤…îx…îya ra, na kanyi danxaniyama Ala xa Di ma, k…în…î mixi naxan mu lama Ala ra, na kanyi bara Ala findi wule fal…õ ra, barima a mu laxi Ala xa seede…≤…îx…îya ra, a naxan baxi a xa Di xa fe ra.
\v 11 Na seede…≤…îx…îya a masenma a Ala kisi fixi won ma a xa Di nan saabui ra. Na kisi mu …≤…înma abadan.
\v 12 Mixi naxan birama Ala xa Di f…îx…î ra, na kanyi bara kisi, k…în…î mixi naxan mu birama Ala xa Di f…îx…î ra, na kanyi mu kisima.
\p 
\v 13 N bara yi fe birin s…õb…õ wo ma, wo tan naxee danxaniyaxi Ala xa Di ma, alako wo xa a kolon a wo bara kisi s…ît…î, naxan mu …≤…înma abadan.
\v 14 Won ma lanlanteya na a ma ki nax…õ, won bara a kolon a won ma duba birin suxuma n…õ naxan findixi a wax…înfe ra.
\v 15 Won to a kolon a won ma maxandi birin m…õma, won man a kolon a Ala won ma duba birin suxuma n…õ.
\p 
\v 16 Mixi naxan a boore nde toma yunubi raba ra, yunubi naxan mu mixi b…în…îma abadan, a xa Ala maxandi a b…õ. Ala a rakisima n…õ xa yunubi na a ra naxan mu mixi b…în…îma abadan. Yunubi nde na naxan mixi b…în…îma abadan. N mu a fala wo xa Ala maxandi na m…î…îli xa fe ra.
\v 17 S…õriy…õ matandife birin findixi yunubi nan na, k…în…î yunubi birin xa mu mixi b…în…îma.
\p 
\v 18 Won a kolon mixi naxan findixi Ala xa di ra, a mu luma yunubi raba ra, barima Ala xa Di, a a kantama. Sentan…õ mu n…îma a ra.
\v 19 Won a kolon a Ala xa die nan won na, k…în…î duni…≤a mixi d…înx…î…õ birin na Sentan…õ sago nan bun ma.
\p 
\v 20 Won man a kolon a Ala xa Di bara fa. A xaxili fanyi nan fixi won ma, alako won xa Ala N…îndi Kanyi kolon. Won nun Ala N…îndi Kanyi nan a ra a xa Di Isa saabui ra, a xa Mixi Sugandixi. A tan nan na Ala N…îndi Kanyi ra, naxan kisi fixi won ma abadan.
\p 
\v 21 N ma die, wo wo y…õt…õ ratanga kuyee ma.
